<i>noun</i>: 충실 [충실], 진정 [진정], 진심 [진심], 진실 [진실], 신실 [신ː실], 성의 [성의/성이], 성심 [성심], 성실성 [성실썽], 성실 [성실] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>충실 [충실]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfulness; devotion; sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>충성스럽고 정직하며 성실함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being loyal, honest, and sincere.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진정 [진정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. truth; sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>거짓이 없는 진실한 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A sincere heart without falsehood.</dd><br>
<dd>2. true reasons</dd><br>
<dd>진실한 사정.</dd><br>
<dd>One's actual circumstances.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진심 [진심]</dt><br>
<dd>truth; sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>거짓이 없는 진실한 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A sincere heart without falsehood.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진실 [진실]</dt><br>
<dd>1. truth</dd><br>
<dd>거짓이 아닌 사실.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that is true, not false.</dd><br>
<dd>2. truth; sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>순수하고 거짓이 없는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A pure and sincere feeling.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>신실 [신ː실]</dt><br>
<dd>sincerity; honesty; faithfulness</dd><br>
<dd>믿음직하고 착실함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being trustworthy and faithful.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성의 [성의/성이]</dt><br>
<dd>sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>정성스러운 뜻.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality or state of being sincere and genuine.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성심 [성심]</dt><br>
<dd>sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>정성스러운 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A sincere heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성실성 [성실썽]</dt><br>
<dd>sincerity; faithfulness</dd><br>
<dd>진실하고 정성스러운 품성.</dd><br>
<dd>A sincere, genuine personality.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>성실 [성실]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfulness; sincerity</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 행동이 진실하고 정성스러움.</dd><br>
<dd>A sincere, genuine attitude or behavior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>